title: Henrik Lundqvist makes 37 saves in Rangers' 5-2 rout of Blue Jackets (NHL - National ...
text: ( Source : NHL - National Hockey League ) NEW YORK , N.Y. - Henrik Lundqvist made 37 saves and Oscar Lindberg scored twice to lead the New York Rangers to a 5-2 win over the Columbus Blue Jackets Saturday night . Dominic Moore , Derick Brassard
